WEBVTT

00:02:01.858 --> 00:02:05.467
By the way you reacted, I can see
your lack of interest.

00:02:05.467 --> 00:02:07.105
(Laughter)

00:02:07.105 --> 00:02:09.116
But that's okay, I understand why.

00:02:09.116 --> 00:02:10.792
We stop thinking too soon.

00:02:10.792 --> 00:02:12.928
But if we give it
a little bit more thought,

00:02:12.928 --> 00:02:14.296
like a paper clip.

00:02:14.296 --> 00:02:19.876
A paper clip makes this a little bit
more interesting.

00:02:19.876 --> 00:02:22.867
Not only that, if instead of using
my hand with the fingers,

00:02:22.867 --> 00:02:24.945
I use my hand closed into a fist,

00:02:24.945 --> 00:02:28.319
that makes this even a little
bit more interesting.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:33.210
Not only that, but I will impose myself
a time limit of one second,